  <!-- ── How to Use Prop Firm Promo Codes ──────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="bg-white border-t border-slate-200 py-16 px-4">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-2">Step-by-Step Guide</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900">How to Use Prop Firm Promo Codes</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Before applying a prop discount code, you need to find a prop trading firm that suits your needs. If you're a new trader, we recommend exploring our
          <a href={`${base}/reviews/`} class="text-teal-600 hover:underline font-medium">best prop firms</a> to compare the top options. If you already have a prop firm in mind,
          visit our full list of <a href={`${base}/reviews/`} class="text-teal-600 hover:underline font-medium">prop firm reviews</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8 mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          It's important to do solid research before you jump into a challenge to ensure you are selecting the best prop firm for your trading style. For instance, you may be looking for futures prop firms, or an instant funding option where you skip evaluation accounts and head straight into the funded trader program.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          You also need to understand the prop firm's profit targets and risk parameters, like daily and max loss, in both the evaluation process and funded account program. Check key trading rules on Expert Advisors and news trading, as these can impact your choice of firm.
        </p>
      </div>

